<hymn_number>289</hymn_number>
<title>Damlai Ni Abeih Ma Hin</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hun kipah um leh Hukdamna ni hin,
 Maban tamtak ka nei,
 Krista sep ban sem di'n;
 Lalpa'n kei ei guot tai.

[V2]
 Damlai ni a beih ma hin,
 Semhat hitiu Lalpa na;
 Hun a dang tai, (2)
 Vaihawmna ni a naitai.

[V3]
 2. Aw ka damlai hun na pammaih ta luoi;
 Thawnin liemlo zen in,
 Hukdampa melsietna;
 Khuh di'n mat ka nuom tai,

[V4]
 3. Tutieng hin Lalpa khawvelah a tawm,
 A tawmna sietlei hi;
 Thisana chawksa nung,
 Amah Lallukhuk di'n.

[V5]
 4. Hun a bei deuh deuh, Hun a buoi deuh deuh,
 Buh tak leh lem sep na'n;
 Tui suohgiet a fawn tai,
 Lalpa thudik na di'n.</lyrics>
</song>